---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-brand-50/60 via-white to-white -z-10"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[800px] h-[600px] bg-brand-500/[0.04] rounded-full blur-3xl -z-10"></div>
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 pt-24 md:pt-32 pb-20">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="animate-fade-in">
          <p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-brand-600 mb-5">Strategic Advisory</p>
          <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight leading-[1.1] text-slate-900">
            I help people and teams figure sh*t out and&nbsp;grow.
          </h1>
          <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-lg leading-relaxed">
            Building a business can get messy fast; too many ideas, not enough clarity. That's where I come in.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-slate-500 max-w-lg leading-relaxed">
            I'm your Strategic Thinking Partner and problem solver; not the kind who makes decks or reports, but the kind who helps you find clarity and move faster on what matters.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-slate-500 max-w-lg leading-relaxed">
            I work with side-hustlers, operators, and founders of distributed teams (usually under twenty people) to bring outside perspective across brand, strategy, community, and operations.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-slate-500 max-w-lg leading-relaxed">
            If you're feeling stuck or unsure what to tackle next, let's talk! The first call's on me. If I can't help, I'll point you to someone who can.
          </p>
          <a href="/contact" class="mt-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-7 py-3.5 bg-brand-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-brand-700 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-brand-200 transition-all duration-200">
            Request a Session →
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="relative">
          <img src="/richard-hero.jpg" alt="Richard Kappel" class="rounded-2xl shadow-layered-lg w-full object-cover aspect-[4/5]" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- First Testimonial -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-slate-50/70">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-layered border border-slate-100" data-animate>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
          <img src="/testimonial-francesco.jpeg" alt="Francesco Rocca" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full object-cover" />
          <div>
            <p class="font-display font-semibold text-slate-900">Francesco Rocca</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Managing Director, Impact Hub Lisbon</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          "Richard's Project Management support, using tools like Trello, Slack, and Google Calendar, transformed our operations at Impact Hub by unifying activities on a single platform and customizing solutions to our needs. His hands-on approach and adaptability were invaluable, fostering a transparent, constructive culture that strengthened team unity. Richard's commitment to understanding both professional and emotional challenges made a significant impact. His guidance and innovative strategies are crucial assets for any organization seeking growth."
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Data Section -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16" data-animate>
        <p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-brand-600 mb-3">The Evidence</p>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900">Businesses with Advisors Outperform</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-slate-500 text-lg">
          Firms that receive structured advisory support consistently grow faster, innovate more, and survive longer than peers without advisors.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-400 font-mono">Global review of peer-reviewed entrepreneurship and SME studies (2000–2025).</p>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-0" data-stagger>
        <div class="group border-t border-slate-200 py-8 grid md:grid-cols-[5rem_1fr] gap-4 md:gap-8 items-start hover:bg-slate-50/50 -mx-4 px-4 md:-mx-8 md:px-8 transition-colors duration-200 rounded-lg">
          <span class="font-mono text-3xl font-bold text-brand-600 pt-1">↑</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors">Advisory Support Improves Survival</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
              U.S. firms that received ongoing counseling from the Small Business Development Centers (SBDCs) showed higher survival and sales growth than comparable non-counseled firms.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="group border-t border-slate-200 py-8 grid md:grid-cols-[5rem_1fr] gap-4 md:gap-8 items-start hover:bg-slate-50/50 -mx-4 px-4 md:-mx-8 md:px-8 transition-colors duration-200 rounded-lg">
          <span class="font-mono text-3xl font-bold text-brand-600 pt-1">50%</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors">Long-Term Profit &amp; Employment Gains</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
              An RCT with 432 Mexican SMEs showed that one year of professional consulting increased returns on assets and total factor productivity, and boosted employment ~50% five years later.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="group border-t border-slate-200 border-b py-8 grid md:grid-cols-[5rem_1fr] gap-4 md:gap-8 items-start hover:bg-slate-50/50 -mx-4 px-4 md:-mx-8 md:px-8 transition-colors duration-200 rounded-lg">
          <span class="font-mono text-3xl font-bold text-amber-500 pt-1">3x</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors">Mentorship Multiplies Startup Success</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
              Startups in accelerator programs with structured mentorship raised three times more funding and hired twice as many employees compared with those that only received cash or workspace.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12 text-center" data-animate="scale">
        <div class="inline-block bg-brand-600 rounded-xl px-10 py-6 text-white">
          <p class="font-display text-lg font-semibold">The Takeaway</p>
          <p class="mt-2 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-brand-100">
            Across industries and continents, advisors aren't a cost — they're a multiplier. The right guidance drives measurable gains in productivity, profitability, growth, and resilience.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-slate-50/70">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16" data-animate>
        <p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-brand-600 mb-3">Services</p>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900">Tailored Solutions</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-slate-500 text-lg">
          Personalized Support for Solopreneurs, Early-Stage Startups, and Hybrid or Fully-remote Teams.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-0" data-stagger>
        {[
          { num: '01', title: 'AI for SMBs', desc: 'Stop renting software. I help you build custom AI tools you own forever.', href: '/ai', tag: 'New' },
          { num: '02', title: 'Business Development', desc: 'Strategic insights to refine and enhance your business growth plans.', href: '/advisory#business-development', tag: null },
          { num: '03', title: 'Project Management', desc: 'External perspective on team dynamics, workflows, and project execution.', href: '/advisory#project-management', tag: null },
          { num: '04', title: 'Community Development', desc: 'Strategies to build and nurture a vibrant community around your business.', href: '/advisory#community-development', tag: null },
          { num: '05', title: 'Brand Positioning', desc: 'Fresh ideas to strengthen and evolve your brand in the marketplace.', href: '/advisory#brand-positioning', tag: null },
          { num: '06', title: 'Personal Mentorship', desc: 'Deeply personal guidance to unlock creative solutions and propel you forward.', href: '/advisory#personal-mentorship', tag: null },
        ].map((service, i) => (
          <a href={service.href} class={`service-item group border-t border-slate-200 ${i === 5 ? 'border-b' : ''} py-6 grid grid-cols-[3rem_1fr_auto] gap-4 md:gap-8 items-center hover:bg-white -mx-4 px-4 md:-mx-8 md:px-8 transition-colors duration-200 rounded-lg cursor-pointer no-underline`}>
            <span class="font-mono text-sm text-slate-300">{service.num}</span>
            <div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors">{service.title}</h3>
                {service.tag && <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-amber-600 bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider">{service.tag}</span>}
              </div>
              <p class="mt-1 text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">{service.desc}</p>
            </div>
            <span class="text-slate-300 group-hover:text-brand-500 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-all duration-200 text-lg">→</span>
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonials -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16" data-animate>
        <p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-brand-600 mb-3">Testimonials</p>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900">What People Say</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6" data-stagger>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-layered">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-5">
            <img src="/testimonial-lauren.jpeg" alt="Lauren Miller" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full object-cover" />
            <div>
              <p class="font-display font-semibold text-slate-900 text-sm">Lauren Miller</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-mono">makesense Lisbon</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            "Richard brought structure, clarity, and energy to the makesense Lisbon community. He co-created a clear strategy, implemented project management systems, and led in-person sessions that united volunteers around a shared vision. His methods made it easy for everyone to understand their role, stay accountable, and develop real skills in leadership and collaboration. Thanks to his approach, the community became more organized, empowered, and connected — even serving as a model for other cities. Richard's ability to combine strategy with human connection is rare. He builds cultures of trust where people feel confident to lead and take action."
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-layered">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-5">
            <img src="/testimonial-pedro.jpeg" alt="Pedro Coelho" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full object-cover" />
            <div>
              <p class="font-display font-semibold text-slate-900 text-sm">Pedro Coelho</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-mono">Founder & CEO, Dumagi</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            "At the beginning of Dumagi's journey, we had the privilege of working with Richard to help us with our brand, and he ended up helping us out with so much more than that. Richard helped us define the direction of our company, structure our digital presence, and build the content that truly reflects who we are today. But his contribution went far beyond strategy, it was deeply human. For me, as founder and CEO, Richard was a true right hand: someone who supported me, believed in the vision, and made me feel that I wasn't walking this path alone. His dedication, insight, and ability to turn ideas into actionable plans made an enormous difference in Dumagi's story."
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-layered md:col-span-2">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-5">
            <img src="/testimonial-camille.png" alt="Camille Bouchard" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full object-cover" />
            <div>
              <p class="font-display font-semibold text-slate-900 text-sm">Camille Bouchard</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-mono">Business Owner</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            "I was initially seeking someone to help me organize and structure my business, but working with Richard exceeded all my expectations. He introduced me to the Notion platform, which he custom-designed to fit my specific needs. With Richard's guidance, I was able to effortlessly organize over 10 years of data—covering collaborators, vendors, clients, projects, and more, allowing me to clear my mind and focus on growth. His expertise has been instrumental in helping me take my business to the next level, including supporting my plans for expansion and hiring new team members. Richard's energy and motivation have given me the confidence and strength to push through the evolution I envisioned for my company."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-slate-50/70">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <img src="/richard-about.jpg" alt="Richard Kappel" class="rounded-2xl shadow-layered-lg w-full object-cover aspect-square" data-animate />
        <div>
          <p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-brand-600 mb-3">About</p>
          <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900">RichKapp</h2>
          <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed" data-animate>
            <p>
              I'm Richard Kappel. At 26, I exited my first company in Chicago. Since then, I've built across industries and continents; launching a hostel, founding a nonprofit that grew into a social enterprise spanning 11 countries with a 40+ person team, and supporting startups from around the world.
            </p>
            <p>
              Through all of it, one thing has been constant: I thrive on solving hard problems and bringing order to chaos.
            </p>
            <p>
              Twenty years in the game taught me one thing: clarity isn't found in books or frameworks. It's built through decisions, mistakes, and the willingness to keep moving when the path isn't clear.
            </p>
            <p>
              Now, I put that experience to work for individuals and teams who want to cut through noise, see what they can't see alone, and move forward with clarity and confidence.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-slate-200 flex flex-wrap gap-2" data-animate>
            <span class="font-mono text-xs text-slate-500 bg-white border border-slate-200 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">20+ Years</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-xs text-slate-500 bg-white border border-slate-200 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">11 Countries</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-xs text-slate-500 bg-white border border-slate-200 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">First Exit at 26</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-xs text-slate-500 bg-white border border-slate-200 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">40+ Person Team</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What I Believe -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16" data-animate>
        <p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-brand-600 mb-3">Principles</p>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900">What I Believe</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-slate-500 text-lg">
          The principles that guide how I work and what I bring to every engagement.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6" data-stagger>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-layered hover:shadow-layered-lg hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-brand-50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">Clarity Over Complexity</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">The best strategies are simple. I help you strip away the noise and focus on what actually matters.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-layered hover:shadow-layered-lg hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-brand-50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">Action Over Analysis Paralysis</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Good decisions made quickly beat perfect decisions made too late. I help you move with confidence.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-layered hover:shadow-layered-lg hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-brand-50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">Human Connection as the Foundation</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Behind every business challenge is a person. I lead with empathy and build relationships grounded in trust.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-layered hover:shadow-layered-lg hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-brand-50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m0 18c-1.657 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.343-9 3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">Outside Perspective as a Multiplier</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">You can't read the label from inside the jar. A fresh set of eyes sees what you've been too close to notice.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How I Work -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-slate-50/70">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16" data-animate>
        <p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-brand-600 mb-3">Process</p>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900">How I Work</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8" data-stagger>
        <div class="group">
          <span class="font-mono text-4xl font-bold text-brand-600">01</span>
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-3">Intro Call</h3>
          <p class="font-mono text-xs text-brand-500 mt-1">45 minutes — on me</p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
            We'll talk through what's on your plate and what "better" looks like. If I'm not the right fit, I'll point you to someone who is.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="group">
          <span class="font-mono text-4xl font-bold text-brand-600">02</span>
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-3">Clarity Sprint</h3>
          <p class="font-mono text-xs text-brand-500 mt-1">2 sessions in ~14 days</p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
            We go deep on the real blockers and priorities. Top 3 priorities (stack-ranked), 90-day focus with next moves, decision rules & metrics to keep you honest. This is where the fog lifts.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="group">
          <span class="font-mono text-4xl font-bold text-brand-600">03</span>
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-3">Momentum Rhythm</h3>
          <p class="font-mono text-xs text-brand-500 mt-1">Ongoing advisory</p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
            Weekly or bi-weekly strategy sessions to keep you moving. Unblock decisions, adjust the plan, and hold the line on focus. No long contracts. I advise; you and your team execute.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-14 text-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-7 py-3.5 bg-brand-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-brand-700 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-brand-200 transition-all duration-200">
          Request a Session →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Build to Own Club -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6" data-animate>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-10 md:p-14 text-center border border-slate-100 shadow-layered">
        <p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-brand-600 mb-4">Community</p>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 mb-6">Build to Own Club</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed max-w-xl mx-auto mb-8">
          You're not alone in this shift. Join a growing community of founders and operators who are taking back control of their software stack — building tools they own, sharing what works, and helping each other move faster.
        </p>
        <a href="https://buildtoown.club" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-7 py-3.5 bg-brand-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-brand-700 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-brand-200 transition-all duration-200">
          Check it Out →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bottom CTA -->
  <section class="py-24 relative overflow-hidden bg-brand-600">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-600 via-brand-700 to-brand-800"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-brand-500/20 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center relative" data-animate>
      <p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-brand-200 mb-4">Let's Talk</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight">Ready to move forward with clarity?</h2>
